Package org.universAAL.context.che.database.impl

Contains the default implementations of the store.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RDF4JBackend
    Implementation of Backend that uses RDF4J to store and retrieve the context events in/from an underlying store server (a SAIL in RDF4J).
    RDF4JBackendCrd
    Extension of RDF4JBackend that uses a modified RDF4J NativeStore that checks cardinality of stored statements, according to OWL Lite (if maxCardinality is 1 only one single value object is accepted).
    RDF4JBackendCrdClc
    Extension of RDF4JBackendCrd that uses a modified RDF4J NativeStore that checks cardinality of stored statements, according to OWL Lite (if maxCardinality is 1 only one single value object is accepted) and also closed collections to avoid situations of collection open-closed duplicity, like:.
    RDF4JBackendCrdClc2
    Extension of RDF4JBackendCrd that uses a modified RDF4J NativeStore that checks cardinality of stored statements, according to OWL Lite (if maxCardinality is 1 only one single value object is accepted) and also closed collections to avoid situations of collection open-closed duplicity, like:.
    RDF4JBackendCrdClc2Cnf
    Like a RDF4JBackendCrdClc2 that interprets the confidence value of received events before storing them.
    RDF4JBackendCrdClcCnf
    Like a RDF4JBackendCrdClc that interprets the confidence value of received events before storing them.
    RDF4JBackendCrdCnf
    Like a RDF4JBackendCrd that interprets the confidence value of received events before storing them.
    RDF4JBackendWithConfidence
    Extension of RDF4JBackend that interprets the confidence value of received events before storing them.
